snippet.title: Carla Yang
snippet.description:
Welcome to my channel! My name is Carla Yang!

Exploring human behavior through the comedy lense of parody making. Focusing on the entertainment industry and pop culture.

Disclaimer: Not trying to make fun of serious issues; My videos are created for entertainment purposes while exploring certain subjects and behaviors. 

I hope you have fun watching my videos! Thanks so much for stopping by and supporting my channel!

Stay safe, stay smart and stay tuned!
